e may perform best\nin terms of improving CTV coverage and organ-at-risk~(OAR) protection. Bayesian\ninference may have a greater impact on handling adaptation cost than increased\nadaptation frequency. The concept of scenario-reduction may be useful to\naddress computational tractability in ART and robust planning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 May 2019 12:48:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-09"}
